## **4. `suricata/_TEMPLATE.rules`**
```suricata
# Name: <Rule descriptive name>
# Description: <Short and precise description of what this rule detects>
# Topic: <IP | Ports | DNS | HTTP>
# Severity: <low | medium | high | critical>
# Refs: <https://reference.link>
# Author: Bastian-Sec
# Date: YYYY-MM-DD

alert <proto> <src_net> <src_port> -> <dst_net> <dst_port> (msg:"<Short message>"; sid:<unique_id>; rev:1; classtype:<class>; priority:<1-4>;)

